snippet.title: Kindred Fates Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Link to our Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/kindredfates/215099457?ref=ahqxds&token=d9349304

Kindred Fates is an open-world monster-battling RPG. Our goal is to expand the monster-battling genre with an original title focused on exploration, a compelling narrative, and fresh game mechanics. If this is a game you want to see, please consider supporting us on Kickstarter!

Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/GCKS8Gx
Website: https://skymillstudios.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SkyMillStudios/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/skymill_stu...
Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/KindredTheGame
